     - parts of a compass
        - how to hold compass
	   - in hand following bearing
	   - in hand - sighting accurately on bearing
	   - FLAT
     - taking a bearing from something
     - following a bearing
     - applying bearing to map (triangulation)
        - orienting map
	- plot bearing - compass, ruler, pencil
     - taking bearing from map
     - Route card workout
        - expedition name/purpose/description/dates/location/times
        - draw route
	   - way markers - name, grid ref, height
	   - segments - length, elevation, terrain/description
	   - travel & pause time estimation
	   - TOTALs distance/elevation/time & summary (difficulty/..)
	   - Turn back/Get outs/Route alternatives
	   - Weather etc 

